  ECHO PLAYER You race up to the top of the slide, sit down and push off! You plummet down the smooth chute and fly off into a small pile of sand!
  ECHO OTHERS %N races up to the top of the slides, sits down and pushes off! "Wheeeeeeeeeeeeee!" %N shouts until %s flys off and lands on %h rear in a pile of sand!
