INUMBER 1294
NAME 1544
WEIGHT 1500
VOLUME 4
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM
This sturdy wooden swing hangs from heavy reinforced ropes attached to a
thick metal frame.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB GO -1
  DISBAND
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You grab a swing to steady it and sit in it.
  ECHO OTHERS %N grabs hold of a swing and sits down in it.
  POSITION SIT
ENDIF
  IFVERB PUSH -1
  IFVAR POSITION = 1
    DISBAND
    CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You pump your legs hard, making the swing move back and forth higher and higher!
      ECHO OTHERS %N pumps %h legs hard, making the swing move back and forth higher and higher!
  ENDIF
  ENDIF
IFVERB PULL -1
IFVAR POSITION = 1
  DISBAND
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You pull back hard on the ropes slowing the swing. You suddenly leap off onto your feet!
  ECHO OTHERS %N pulls back hard on the ropes slowing the swing. %N suddenly leaps off the swing onto %h feet with a silly grin on %h face.
  POSITION STAND
ENDIF
ENDIF
