NUMBER 580
NAME School Foyer
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Soft light, cast by the amber paned lanterns suspended high overhead, glints
on the highly polished oak floors in this small foyer. Pastel flower petals
surround a plaque at the base of a tall sculpture centered in the middle of
of the room. As the shadows shift and change the figures depicted in the
colorful murals on the two side walls seem to move as if alive. An oak door
leads back outside.
*DESCRIPTION_END
