Behind the glass top of the coffee table you see a framed picture of the
Institute of Enlightenment's student body.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The bookcase is filled with books, most of them bound in paper.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 5
The books have various titles. Many of them seem to be along the lines of
"Educating the Ridiculously Gifted", but there is a sprinkling of novels,
books about a Saint, about someone named Nero Wolfe, a series of chess books,
fantasies by authors like Lord Dunsany and JRR Tolkien, and a few bound
examples of Lukas's own work unless some other deCamerons have published
their writings.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
It's a framed poster of a series of strangely dressed characters on a
starscape. One of them, a young man, is wielding a light sabre. Above the
graphic are the words STAR WARS.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Smells like the school dogs are allowed in here.
  ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs the air as %s glances around the room.
ENDIF
IFVERB GET 5
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER But, that would be stealing!
  ECHO OTHERS As %N starts to grab a book %s gets a guilty look on %h face and quickly replaces it.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2608
NAME deCameron Bedroom
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Great Gods, what a mess! This is the bedroom and work area of Lukas Brian
deCameron, boy wonder. Articles of clothing and comic books litter the
floor tumbled together with the bedding which dangles off a rumpled bed..
Piles of papers cover a small desk and a archway, filled with mist, leads
out.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 199 ADJ1=216 VAL2=2607
ITEM 1 84
ITEM 2 201 ADJ1=294
ITEM 3 60 ADJ1=197
ITEM 4 1289
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
It's a mess. Lukas sleeps on it, when he sleeps here, along with a dog
sometimes. You wanna know more, you can darn well ask him! I mean, even
teenagers need their privacy, y'know?
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Sifting through the papers, it looks as if Lukas is working on administering
the Institute, protecting Fayd's kids, and returning the spirits of children
sent too early to their deaths. He seems to write a lot and often to fairly
important persons.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The arch is covered with strange runes and filled with mist.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 4
They are in an unknown tongue.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB RECALL -1
ECHO PLAYER  You recognize that these runes are linked to faerie somehow. The arch reminds you of those in Belinda's faerie realm.
ENDIF
IFVERB GO 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Somehow, you are prevented from entering.
  ECHO OTHERS %N reaches out and touches the mist, but doesn't enter the arch.
ENDIF
  IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Yup, the school dogs are allowed in here, too.
    ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs around as if looking for something.
  ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2609
NAME Narrow Stairway
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
A covered narrow wooden stairway leads almost straight up the side of this
home and ends at the doorway to a small peaked room. Flowered vines curl
around the posts and railing, lining the way with a profusion of purple
blossoms. A rosewood door leads back into the main house.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1226 ADJ1=583 VAL2=2861
ITEM 1 1050 ADJ1=355
ITEM 2 664 ADJ1=152
IFVERB SNIFF -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER There is a fragrant heady scent lingering in the air.
  ECHO OTHERS %N takes a few deeps breaths before ascending the steep steps.
ENDIF
IFVERB CLIMB 0
  ECHO PLAYER You run up the steps, throw open the door and rush into the room before you trip and fall down the stairs!
  ECHO OTHERS %N runs up the steps, throws open the door and rushes into the room!
ENDIF
