NUMBER 2861
NAME Starshine's Room
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
A explosion of color fills the room, created by the flowers which seem to
cover almost every inch of space. Upon closer inspection you notice that
part of the illusion is created by floral patterned wallpaper, which completely
covers the walls and ceiling. The same pattern is repeated in the quilt
and pillows covering a shiny brass bed and the thick rug. Numerous vases,
placed upon the small round tables scattered about, hold huge bouquets of
fragrant flowers.
*DESCRIPTION_END
